LANE BROS. CO. et al. v. WILCOX MFG. CO. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 26, 1907.) No. 219. Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. A. Parker Smith, for appellants. C. E. Pickard, A. H. Adams, J. L. Jackson, and H. A. Heyn, for appellees.

Before LACOMBE, TOWNSEND, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree (141 Fed. 1000) affirmed, with costs.
